==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dabster
<hw>Dab"ster</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. <er>Dab</er> an
expert.]</ety> <def>One who is skilled; a master of his business; a
proficient; an adept.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ Sometimes improperly used for <xex>dabbler</xex>; as,
⟦ldquo⟧I am but a <xex>dabster</xex> with gentle art⟦rdquo⟧.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dacapo</ent>⟦br⟧
